{"tid":2385501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［好嬲好嬲］譚耀宗：嚴厲譴責傳媒滋擾家人","createTime":"2021-01-29T05:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:50:35.000Z","uid":290118,"like":171,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8b1bf2bc5ca4e29133ecd84ea8bf408e0eca5f","tid":2385501,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"支那01<br />\n有傳媒報道，全國人大常委譚耀宗的長子譚建宏及兒媳梁仲萍已入籍澳洲，於當地開設審計及企業諮詢服務公司，從事移民顧問生意，提供香港及內地人移民服務。報道又指，梁仲萍於2014年已夥拍當地移民公司，回內地舉辦移民講座。<br />\n譚耀宗回覆《香港01》查詢時表示，尊重兒媳選擇的生活和工作，批訐壹傳媒集團立場偏頗，「長期以來攻撃愛國愛港人士，今次更進一步滋擾到我的家人，我感到十分憤慨，並要予以嚴厲譴責！」"},{"pid":"d57aef8494e6b00dc1f3707d504aa6eca72f9720","tid":2385501,"uid":51271,"like":227,"dislike":3,"score":224,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"你攪人就得呀賣國賊"},{"pid":"240f982b65ac743f891b4adebcb2564d865ba992","tid":2385501,"uid":78243,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔係果度出現就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f904f558fb4f9b58fd97acb39caf8ab5b0c7c1","tid":2385501,"uid":77625,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"無搞你 只係把事實講出黎 係愛國愛港表現"},{"pid":"26f327c0340b0c2d0a65734d081a5a32ddda5233","tid":2385501,"uid":41343,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"外國好撚危險架，叫你屋企人返嚟啦"},{"pid":"85375630eaf9230c4beb93b547e506e17ee89965","tid":2385501,"uid":51271,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"係唔係收咗澳洲佬錢，講！"},{"pid":"50e8a0d9ee8459855abe58235dcbf7e93d734938","tid":2385501,"uid":87737,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"賣得國就預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13844c07fa22110b99ec6e0569bf920ef7ae6ccd","tid":2385501,"uid":77196,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime